Latisha Fisher, 35, has been charged with second-degree murder for allegedly smothering her 20-month-old son Gavriel Ortiz-Fisher with her bare hands inside a bathroom at 5 Boro Burger in Midtown Manhattan .
Fisher had a violent past and a history of psychiatric problems, but was evaluated as recently as last year .
She was diagnosed with schizophrenia after a 2011 stabbing .